mosh on MacOS X
===============

1. Install
----------

- Install following using MacPorts:
  oniguruma5
  gmp
- ./configure CFLAGS=-I/opt/local/include LDFLAGS=-L/opt/local/lib
- make

Alternatively, you can use CMake and XCode. See README.CMake for details.

2. Limitations
--------------

- Configure script may fail to recognise target architecture. set
  CC=i686-darwin10-gcc CXX=i686-darwin10-c++ or so to avoid this problem.
